# Business Intelligence Integration

## Overview

This folder contains the Business Intelligence (BI) integration layer of the SAP S/4HANA-inspired ERP implementation.

The BI layer consolidates data and insights from the FI, CO, SD, MM, and Analytics modules into unified dashboards and reporting solutions that support operational monitoring and executive decision-making.

## Scope

The implementation focuses on integrating data across all modules and presenting business performance through interactive dashboards, KPIs, and automated reports.

Key areas include:

* Executive Dashboard
* Financial Performance Dashboard
* Operational Analytics Dashboard
* Procurement and Inventory Reporting
* Automated Business Reporting

## SAP References

The project is inspired by analytics and reporting capabilities commonly associated with:

* SAP Analytics Cloud (SAC)
* SAP BusinessObjects
* SAP Embedded Analytics

